    "Given the weights W ðnÞ ij and thresholds ϑ ðnÞ i of the SNN, the weight matrices w (n) and bias vectors b (n) of the equivalent ReLU network are:",
    "where M is a function that maps the weights W ðnÞ ij of the TTFS network to the weights w ðnÞ ij of the ReLU network with the parameter B ðnÞ i defined in Eq.",
    "Then, for the vector x (0) of input activations, the reverse mapping in Eq.",
